On Wed, 29 May 2002, Greg Thompson wrote:

> Ok I just got the truck back and it was a bad ball joint (even though it
> was brand new)...the shop said that even with all the tie rods removed and
> the truck up in the air, they could barely move the left wheel by hand (as
> if steering).  It drives great now and all is well.  Thanks to everyone who
